{"tid":1563570,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[提議] IFC光復行動好波！如果有埋呢三樣野就完美啦","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:25:54.000Z","uid":270506,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"492cd9971b292d66922ebf54e9f1ac0aa409ab71","tid":1563570,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:35:25.000Z","msg":"就係<strong>英文口號</strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">美國國歌</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國國旗</span></strong>🇺🇸<br />\n<br />\n中環咁多鬼佬，而且頭先有外媒在場，但英文口號唔算多，而且冇美國國旗 (美國國歌唔知有冇播，遲左黎到），感覺又浪費左次宣傳機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信各位而家都知持續向美國表示支持人權法案係幾咁重要，尤其中共呢排開始打國際牌，叫左兩個八婆去UN之後應該唔少得搵人lobby 美國嘅議員，阻礙人權法案通過。大家如果唔持續向美國人表示支持人權法案，中共有機會反cup 成功，第時大家就集中營見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國歌同願榮光歸香港一首接一首咁播，可以營造美港同盟嘅畫面，加強宣傳效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩帶speaker 嘅巴絲打要準備埋美國國歌，大家聽到美國國歌請記得肅立，擺低手機右手放心口，對待盟邦國旗國歌要帶尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"9c29bee932ac283fd69b98565b65f089367d85c5","tid":1563570,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%